### Confirm Reservation (Admin)
# Remplace RESERVATION_ID et YOUR_CLERK_TOKEN
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/reservations/RESERVATION_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_TOKEN

{
  "action": "confirm"
}

